EN: Religious customs hold significant importance in many cultures.

ZH: 每个宗教都有其独特的教义和戒律。
EN: Every religion has its own unique doctrines and rules.

ZH: 宗教仪式会让人们感到神圣和庄严。
EN: Religious ceremonies make people feel sacred and solemn.

ZH: 宗教文化是世界文明的重要组成部分。
EN: Religious culture is an important part of world civilization.

ZH: 宗教信仰可以给人们带来希望和力量。
